  "title": "Create: Now Recipe",
  "description": "This mod adds several recipes to the Create mod.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a9253d2c8a6483880cb482670f2cd35420051e1a.png\" \n    width=\"600%\"\n    style=\"border: 3px solid #444; border-radius: 8px; padding: 5px;\"\n  >\n</p>\n\n<br><br>\n\n<!-- ABOUT IMAGE -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2db6ed996440ba465b2052b4f8d586a0cdb2ac6a.png\" width=\"15%\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\nThis mod is similar to Create: Stones,<br>\nCreate: More Recipes Addon, Create: Ultimate Factory, and other similar mods.<br>\nThis mod includes recipes for items such as:<br>\n<br> 1. Diamonds <br> 2. Netherite <br> 3. Ochrum <br> 4. Cremsite <br> and other similar materials.\n</p>\n\n<!-- CREDITS IMAGE -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ebe5470dad5c13aa44eeb2a71468e23059d9d88d.png\" width=\"20%\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\nDeveloper: EFUJE<br>\nBased on the Create mod<br>\nThanks to everyone who supports the project ❤️\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\nIf you find a bag, please contact me using the email below.\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\nEmail: 5jg4zsi26@mozmail.com\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/efuje_mods\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e806d244c7919a6aa1538477562f8733e1ff6bd6.png\" width=\"9%\">\n  </a>\n\n  <!-- <a href=\"YOUR_DISCORD_LINK\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8fbe5e284a422960404ead08cd8314905aaa2aef.png\" width=\"9%\">\n  </a> \n\n  <a href=\"YOUR_YOUTUBE_LINK\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7f89bb640a7763028cbbceb9ced3d4ca8dce29af.png\" width=\"9%\">\n  </a> -->\n\n  <a href=\"https://buymeacoffee.com/efuje_mods\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2ce9f7cc529769cec0ddcc9ad7b81de9f609c9ba.png\" width=\"9%\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- OUR OTHER PROJECTS\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/02a7d66353b8f12d948f6773503bdf396d4dd960.png\" width=\"50%\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\nHere you will find my other mods and addons.\n</p> -->\n<br>",
